- BUT RALPH, YOU'RE GOING
A HUNDRED AND THIRTY

25
00:02:01,208 --> 00:02:02,708
LIGHT YEARS AWAY.

26
00:02:03,708 --> 00:02:05,750
I'LL BE DEAD BY THE
TIME YOU EVEN GET THERE.

27
00:02:05,833 --> 00:02:08,375
