- SARA.

29
00:02:13,250 --> 00:02:15,208
- ( music box playing )

30
00:02:15,291 --> 00:02:16,875
- ( crying )

31
00:02:16,958 --> 00:02:18,291
- ( watch beeps )

32
00:02:23,791 --> 00:02:26,166
- SARA. I HAVE TO GO.

33
00:02:32,125 --> 00:02:33,541
I WILL RETURN.

34
00:02:40,125 --> 00:02:41,083
- WAIT!

35
00:02:43,125 --> 00:02:46,875
- I WANT TO...
I WANT TO FOLLOW YOU, BROTHER.

36
00:02:47,875 --> 00:02:48,833
- SARA.

37
00:02:55,541 --> 00:02:57,625
ONCE YOU'VE DECIDED
WHAT YOU WANT IN LIFE,

38
00:02:57,708 --> 00:02:59,083
IT'S UP TO YOU TO ACCOMPLISH IT.

39
00:02:59,166 --> 00:03:00,875
AS LONG AS YOU
BELIEVE IN YOURSELF,

40
00:03:00,958 --> 00:03:02,791
THERE'S NOTHING YOU CAN'T DO.

41
00:03:02,875 --> 00:03:03,833
- HMM.

42
00:03:05,458 --> 00:03:06,416
- I'LL SEE YOU.

43
00:03:12,541 --> 00:03:16,208
- WE WILL BE TOGETHER AGAIN,
BUT IT WON'T BE HERE.

44
00:03:16,291 --> 00:03:18,166
I'M ONE STEP
BEHIND YOU, BROTHER.

45
00:03:39,833 --> 00:03:40,833
- HERE GOES NOTHING.

46
00:03:55,208 --> 00:03:57,333
I SWEAR IT GETS EASIER
EVERY TIME.

47
00:03:58,791 --> 00:04:02,375
- SARA. WHAT IS WITH YOU TODAY?
YOU'RE UNSTOPPABLE!

48
00:04:02,458 --> 00:04:04,708
- AREN'T I ALWAYS?

49
00:04:04,791 --> 00:04:06,958
- OKAY, SARA,
I'M ALL FOR YOU BEING AN ACE,

50
