( giggles )

224
00:12:04,833 --> 00:12:05,791
- Mary: HOW ARE THEY DOING?

225
00:12:06,916 --> 00:12:08,958
- Colin: THEY'RE DANCING AGAIN.

226
00:12:09,041 --> 00:12:12,875
- UH, KEEPING TRACK OF THEM
IS LIKE WATCHING PAINT DRY.

227
00:12:12,958 --> 00:12:15,791
HONESTLY, HE COULD AT LEAST
HOLD ONTO HER SHOULDER.

228
00:12:15,875 --> 00:12:18,375
- HOW MUCH ARE YOU WILLING
TO BET IF WE ASK CEDIE,

229
00:12:18,458 --> 00:12:21,000
HE'LL SAY JUST BEING CLOSE
TO HER IS ENOUGH FOR HIM?

230
00:12:21,083 --> 00:12:23,208
- HE JUST NEEDS TO WORK UP
SOME COURAGE ALREADY.

231
00:12:25,000 --> 00:12:27,666
- ( clock chiming )

232
00:12:29,833 --> 00:12:31,041
- WHAT IN THE WORLD?

233
00:12:32,708 --> 00:12:35,250
- LOOKS LIKE THEY'RE DOING
SOME NIGHT TIME EXERCISES.

234
00:12:52,416 --> 00:12:54,041
- ( siren wailing )
- Dorincourt: THE DEAGUE

235
00:12:54,125 --> 00:12:56,166
ARE ATTACKING GRABERA?
HOW CAN THAT BE?

236
00:12:56,250 --> 00:12:59,083
WHY WOULD THEY STRIKE SO
FAR BEHIND THE FRONT LINES?

237
00:12:59,166 --> 00:13:01,125
THIS IS A TRAINING FACILITY!

238
00:13:01,208 --> 00:13:04,291
- WE CAN'T CONTACT CENTRAL
COMMAND! EVERY LINK IS DOWN!

239
00:13:04,375 --> 00:13:05,500
- LOOKS LIKE THE FEEDS ARE GONE

240
00:13:05,583 --> 00:13:06,916
FROM THE GEODETIC
SATELLITES TOO.

241
00:13:07,000 --> 00:13:09,208
DOES ANYONE KNOW WHAT THE
ORBITAL FORCES ARE DOING?

242
00:13:09,291 --> 00:13:11,708
- WE'RE GETTING REPORTS
OF TUMORS ATTACKING CIVILIANS!

243
00:13:11,791 --> 00:13:13,833
- ( loud explosion )

244
00:13:15,708 --> 00:13:18,708
- THE DORMS WERE JUST HIT!
- QUICKLY! EVACUATE THE CADETS!

245
00:13:18,791 --> 00:13:20,416
WE CAN'T ALLOW
ANYMORE TO PERISH!

246
00:13:20,500 --> 00:13:22,541
HOBBS, LISTEN,
I WANT YOU TO TAKE COMMAND!

247
00:13:22,625 --> 00:13:25,125
- RIGHT. ALL FREE
HANDS FOLLOW ME!

248
00:13:25,208 --> 00:13:26,416
- YES, SIR!
- HAVISHAM!

249
00:13:26,500 --> 00:13:28,333
- I'M GOING TO PILOT A STRAIN!

250
00:13:28,416 --> 00:13:29,875
- WHAT'S GOING ON UP THERE?

251
00:13:41,041 --> 00:13:42,416
- ( screaming )

252
00:13:43,333 --> 00:13:44,291
- ( gasps )

253
00:13:45,791 --> 00:13:47,875
- ( gasps ) CEDIE! LOOK!

254
00:13:52,458 --> 00:13:54,625
- TUMORS.
- NO WAY.

255
00:13:54,708 --> 00:13:57,375
HOW DID THEY SLIP THROUGH
THE SECURITY DEFENSES?

256
00:13:57,458 --> 00:13:58,833
SARA! WHERE'RE YOU GOING?

257
00:13:58,916 --> 00:14:01,291
- WHERE DO YOU THINK?
I'M GOING TO GO GET MY STRAIN!

258
00:14:01,375 --> 00:14:02,458
- ARE YOU OUT OF YOUR MIND?

259
00:14:10,500 --> 00:14:12,875
- Sara: THANK GOODNESS!
THE GARDEN HASN'T BEEN HIT YET!

260
00:14:14,083 --> 00:14:15,916
- ( siren wailing )

261
00:14:19,083 --> 00:14:22,250
- HEY, GUYS. ARE YOU OKAY?
- WHAT TOOK YOU SO LONG?

262
00:14:22,333 --> 00:14:24,083
- HURRY UP! LET'S GET OUT THERE!

263
00:14:24,166 --> 00:14:27,458
- COMMAND'S DOWN,
SO WE'RE GOING TO BE ON OUR OWN.

264
00:14:27,541 --> 00:14:29,166
- I CAN'T BELIEVE
THE TUMORS WERE ABLE TO

265
00:14:29,250 --> 00:14:31,333
GET SO CLOSE TO US WITHOUT
SETTING OFF ANY ALARMS.

266
00:14:31,416 --> 00:14:32,958
THAT MEANS SOMEONE
MUST HAVE BETRAYED US

267
00:14:33,041 --> 00:14:34,583
AND GAVE AWAY OUR
POSITION TO THE DEAGUE!

268
00:14:34,666 --> 00:14:36,916
- WELL THERE'S NO POINT
IN DISCUSSING IT RIGHT NOW.

269
00:14:37,000 --> 00:14:39,291
WE NEED ALL OUR ATTENTION
ON REPELLING THE ATTACK.

270
00:14:41,500 --> 00:14:42,458
( gasps )

271
00:15:06,541 --> 00:15:07,500
- Mary: HERE THEY COME.

272
00:15:08,500 --> 00:15:10,666
THERE ARE THOUSANDS OF THEM.

273
00:15:10,750 --> 00:15:13,000
- HOW ARE WE GOING TO DO THIS?
WE'RE OUTNUMBERED.

274
00:15:13,916 --> 00:15:15,541
- SARA.

275
00:15:15,625 --> 00:15:16,750
- DON'T WORRY, CEDIE.

276
00:15:16,833 --> 00:15:18,916
THIS'LL BE JUST LIKE THE
TRAINING EXERCISES.

277
00:15:19,000 --> 00:15:21,375
BESIDES, THERE'S NO WAY
WE CAN LET THESE BASTARDS,

278
00:15:21,458 --> 00:15:22,791
KILL US ON OUR OWN TURF!

279
00:15:22,875 --> 00:15:24,958
- LET'S DO IT!
- All: ROGER!

280
00:15:27,083 --> 00:15:28,791
- ( Sara yells )

281
00:15:37,958 --> 00:15:41,000
- ( Cedie gasps ) WHAT IS THAT?

282
00:15:41,083 --> 00:15:44,791
NO WAY, IT CAN'T BE.
A GLOIRE STRAIN?

283
00:15:44,875 --> 00:15:46,583
- Colin: IT'S ABOUT TIME
ONE OF THEM SHOWED UP.

284
00:15:46,666 --> 00:15:48,750
WE'RE GOING TO NEED ALL THE
HELP WE CAN GET WITH THIS.

285
00:15:48,833 --> 00:15:50,750
- NO. IT'S BAD.

286
00:15:52,125 --> 00:15:53,208
- Colin: WHAT DO YOU MEAN?

287
00:15:56,791 --> 00:15:58,291
- ( all gasping )

288
00:16:01,916 --> 00:16:02,875
- ( Mary screams )

289
00:16:05,000 --> 00:16:08,208
- WHAT IS SHE... SARA! DON'T!

290
00:16:08,291 --> 00:16:09,875
- ( yelling )

291
00:16:16,625 --> 00:16:17,583
DAMN YOU!

292
00:16:20,500 --> 00:16:21,458
( gasps )

293
00:16:23,125 --> 00:16:24,083
- Cedie: RUN!

294
00:16:25,375 --> 00:16:26,583
SARA!

295
00:16:30,083 --> 00:16:31,375
- CEDIE!

296
00:16:50,750 --> 00:16:53,041
I THINK I REMEMBER THERE
BEING AN OLD ARMY LAB

297
00:16:53,125 --> 00:16:54,208
IN THAT DIRECTION.

298
00:16:54,291 --> 00:16:56,541
( gasps ) IS THAT WHAT
THEY'RE HERE FOR?

299
00:16:56,625 --> 00:16:58,666
- ( siren wailing )

300
00:17:25,833 --> 00:17:27,791
- ( panting )

301
00:17:32,958 --> 00:17:34,291
THE REASONER'S INSIDE!

302
00:18:02,125 --> 00:18:04,916
- ( heavy breathing )

303
00:18:25,791 --> 00:18:27,541
- ( panting )

304
00:18:34,375 --> 00:18:35,333
( gasps )

305
00:18:38,083 --> 00:18:40,083
( crying )

306
00:18:40,916 --> 00:18:41,916
COLIN.

307
00:18:42,500 --> 00:18:43,458
MARY.

308
00:18:44,958 --> 00:18:46,166
CEDIE.

309
00:18:46,250 --> 00:18:48,125
( crying )

310
00:18:49,750 --> 00:18:52,041
- ( footsteps approaching )

311
00:18:55,416 --> 00:18:56,375
- IT'S HIM!

312
00:19:04,875 --> 00:19:06,500
( panting )

313
00:19:08,166 --> 00:19:09,125
THERE!

314
00:19:14,666 --> 00:19:16,625
STOP! DON'T MOVE, YOU TRAITOR!

315
00:19:20,791 --> 00:19:22,541
YOU'RE SUPPOSED TO BE ONE OF US!

316
00:19:22,625 --> 00:19:24,875
WHY WOULD YOU
BETRAY US LIKE THAT?

317
00:19:24,958 --> 00:19:26,500
YOU KILLED EVERYONE!

318
00:19:26,583 --> 00:19:28,875
THE SCHOOL. MY FRIENDS.

319
00:19:29,666 --> 00:19:34,708
COLIN. MARY. CEDIE.

320
00:19:34,791 --> 00:19:37,291
YOU BASTARD!
YOU'LL PAY FOR THIS!

321
00:19:44,500 --> 00:19:45,458
( gasps )

322
00:19:55,208 --> 00:19:56,916
( crying )

323
00:19:58,250 --> 00:19:59,208
RALPH?

324
00:20:14,500 --> 00:20:15,416
- ( gasps )

325
00:20:24,250 --> 00:20:25,208
- BROTHER!

326
00:20:27,583 --> 00:20:28,541
( gasps )

327
00:20:38,458 --> 00:20:39,500
I NEED TO BORROW THIS.

328
00:20:46,750 --> 00:20:47,708
BROTHER!

329
00:20:49,000 --> 00:20:51,916
BROTHER, WHAT'S WRONG?
WHY ARE YOU DOING THIS?

330
00:20:53,666 --> 00:20:54,625
( screams )

331
00:20:56,791 --> 00:20:57,750
( gasps )

332
00:21:44,666 --> 00:21:47,000
( crying )

333
00:21:52,208 --> 00:21:54,166
( screaming )

334
00:22:06,333 --> 00:22:08,541
- ( theme song playing )

335
00:22:08,625 --> 00:22:10,208
- (singing in Japanese)

336
00:23:37,875 --> 00:23:39,750
- Sara: ALL HOPE ISN'T LOST YET.

337
00:23:39,833 --> 00:23:41,125
IT'S NOT THE PATH I INTENDED,

338
00:23:41,208 --> 00:23:43,125
BUT IT WILL GET ME TO
WHERE MY BROTHER IS.

339
00:23:43,208 --> 00:23:45,541
I'M WILLING TO DO
WHATEVER IT TAKES!

340
00:23:45,625 --> 00:23:48,500
NEXT TIME ON STRAIN, ENCOUNTER.

341
00:23:48,583 --> 00:23:49,791
IS THIS MY FATE?

